      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAVTIMEMAJOR NZ (5) is a gelding by leading sire Art Major on debut for the Chantal Turpin stable. Has strong trial form coming into this, winning his last two hitouts at this circuit and distance. Looks talented and will be ready to go. ILLBERIDINGSHOTGUN (6) has the hoof on the till after finishing second in his two outings at this circuit and distance so far, missing narrowly last week. Draws wider but gets the experience edge on a few of these and a win looks imminent. SIMPLY INSPIRING (1) was beaten 5 metres on debut last week but will strip fitter and is well served by the ace draw. FIT AND READY (3) is by champion sire Bettors Delight and hails from the Grant Dixon stable. Dam has produced Group 1 winner Fire And Passion. Has shown enough at the trials to anticipate a bright start to her career.",
